name: Botanical Deep Dive no.1
description:
Deep dive into the botanical illustrations of Ernst Haeckel. This particular work zooms us into the piece "Table 72: Muscinae. - Laubmoose / A. Giltsch, gem." from 1904. New ai-powered details emerge as the viewer travels into the work. Perfect loop. Part of the "deep dive" series. Rendered with a neural style transfer process.
